      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_2195313dfcac8b8c6cedef16d2578cfc">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The prints are arranged numerically according to the numbering of their corresponding
            Megilot ha-esh [Scrolls of Fire] verses. The chapter titles from the English
            translations of Kovner's verses follow the chapter numbers in the folder listing.</p>
      </arrangement>
